code: /**  * Unmarshals the given provided {@link Source} into an object graph,  * reading binary attachments from a {@link MimeContainer}.  * @param source the source to marshal from  * @param mimeContainer the MIME container to read extracted binary content from  * @return the object graph  * @throws XmlMappingException if the given source cannot be mapped to an object  * @throws IOException if an I/O Exception occurs  */ Object unmarshal(Source source, @Nullable MimeContainer mimeContainer) throws XmlMappingException, IOException.
